OL,3,CHundreds of bus workers in Wales set
OL,4,Cto strike over pay
OL,6,FHundreds of bus workers across Wales
OL,7,Fare to take strike action over pay.
OL,9,FUnite the Union members are set to
OL,10,Ftake industrial action in October
OL,11,Fafter they say the bus company First
OL,12,FCymru "refused to offer a back dated
OL,13,Fpay rise."
OL,15,FDrivers, cleaners, engineers, stores
OL,16,Fworkers and administrative staff in
OL,17,Fdepots across Wales will be walking
OL,18,Fout for four days in October with the
OL,19,Fthreat of more strikes if the dispute
OL,20,Fis not resolved.
