OL,3,CHundreds of bus workers in Wales set
OL,4,Cto strike over pay
OL,6,FMembers of Unite rejected a 5% pay
OL,7,Frise, saying "the employer was trying
OL,8,Fto withhold 60% of owed back pay."
OL,10,FThey also complain of lower wages for
OL,11,Fnew recruits "creating a two-tier
OL,12,Fworkforce that sows unhappiness among
OL,13,Fstaff."
OL,15,FThe strikes at depots in Swansea, Port
OL,16,FTalbot, Bridgend, Carmarthen,
OL,17,FHaverfordwest and Ammanford are due to
OL,18,Ftake place between 22-25 October.
