OL,3,CHundreds of bus workers in Wales set
OL,4,Cto strike over pay
OL,6,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,7,Fsaid: "First Group is a hugely
OL,8,Fprofitable company making millions yet
OL,9,Fit is treating its workers, and the
OL,10,Fcommunities they come from in Wales,
OL,11,Fwith utter disdain.
OL,13,F"It is simply unacceptable to pay
OL,14,Fpoverty wages, offer a paltry pay rise
OL,15,Fand then try and withhold back pay.
OL,16,FOur members won't stand for it and
OL,17,Fthey have the full support of their
OL,18,Funion in this dispute."
