OL,3,CHundreds of bus workers in Wales set
OL,4,Cto strike over pay
OL,6,FStaff are demanding a pay award of #15
OL,7,Fper hour, which they say would bring
OL,8,Fthem in line with Cardiff Bus and
OL,9,FArriva in North Wales.
OL,11,FDoug Claringbold, Managing Director
OL,12,Ffor First Bus in Cymru, said: "We are
OL,13,Fdisappointed for our customers that
OL,14,Fthe above inflation pay offer we have
OL,15,Fmade to colleagues has been rejected
OL,16,Fand that they will now face disruption
OL,17,Facross south and west Wales.
