OL,3,CHundreds of bus workers in Wales set
OL,4,Cto strike over pay
OL,6,F"Throughout an extensive negotiation
OL,7,Fprocess we have listened to Unite
OL,8,Fmember feedback and made a number of
OL,9,Foffers in order to try and reach an
OL,10,Fagreement so that customers who rely
OL,11,Fon our services are not affected by
OL,12,Fstrike action.
OL,14,F"Unfortunately, the union has decided
OL,15,Fto press ahead with strikes over the
OL,16,Fcoming weeks, including during the
OL,17,Fhalf term holiday. Our door remains
OL,18,Fopen to continue discussions and avoid
OL,19,Funnecessary disruption.
